Hadronization: To cover the choice of parton shower and hadronization models, samples produced with the Powheg-Box program are showered with either the Pythia6 program using the P2011C tune or the Herwig and Jimmy programs using the ATLAS AUET2 tune. This includes different approaches in shower modelling, such as using a pT\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
